      • getEnrollmentStatus

        String getEnrollmentStatus()
        Gets the enrollment status. Possible values are:
        • AM: Not Started/Admitted
        • F: Full-time
        • H: Half-time or more, but less than full-time
        • L: Less than half-time
        • A: Approved Leave of Absence
        • X: Never Attended
        • C: Cancel
        • G: Graduated
        • D: Deceased
        • W: Withdrawn (voluntary or involuntary)
        • RE: Re-entry Required
        • AC: Academic Complete
